---
import Section from '../Section.astro';
import H2 from '../H2.astro';
import H3 from '../H3.astro';
import Text from '../Text.astro';
---
<Section id="faq" class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid bg-grid-pattern bg-grid-transition-top"></div>
    <div class="z-1 relative mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-screen-md xl:max-w-screen-lg">
        <H2 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</H2>
        <div class="space-y-8 mt-12 lg:mt-16">
            <div>
                <H3>How long does it take to build my website?</H3>
                <Text class="mt-4">Single-page websites take 1–2 weeks. Multi-page websites (4–8 pages) take 3–6 weeks. Large or custom websites can take 6–12 weeks. We provide a clear timeline during the Discovery phase.</Text>
            </div>
            <div>
                <H3>Can I update the website myself?</H3>
                <Text class="mt-4">Yes, except for the Starter package. We provide a CMS or short tutorial for content management so you can handle updates easily.</Text>
            </div>
            <div>
                <H3>What happens after launch?</H3>
                <Text class="mt-4">We offer post-launch support, bug fixes, improvements, and optional maintenance packages to ensure your site stays healthy.</Text>
            </div>
            <div>
                <H3>Can I request custom features?</H3>
                <Text class="mt-4">Yes. We can integrate booking systems, payment gateways, APIs, advanced forms, and more depending on your brand's needs.</Text>
            </div>
            <div>
                <H3>Do I need to provide my own hosting and domain?</H3>
                <Text class="mt-4">If you already have them, we can use your setup. Otherwise, we will recommend suitable options and handle everything for you.</Text>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Section>